{"word":"ἀνακτάομαι","slug":"ἀνακτάομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀνακτάομαι</b></el> <p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a>, <i>to regain for oneself, get back again, recover</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> <a href='S:person, personal'>pers.</a> <i>to win</i> a person <i>over, gain</i> his <i>favour</i> or <i>friendship</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}